Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是巴麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.47,0:00:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你们一样是见泷原中学的三年级学生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是同丘比订下了契约的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法少女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又做了奇怪的梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小圆
